Name: Eagle Simulator
About the game: If you've ever wondered what it's like to be a bird, then Eagle Simulator is just for you! Your mission is to be as fast as an eagle, but you have to be careful because any mistake will cost you. Game Features: - 5 eagle to choose at your own - Multiple scenes to fly - Quickly changes of the weather
